sentences.english: Senior middle school chemistry teaching should be conducted with the concept of new curriculum reform.
sentences.chinese: 高中化學教學需要用新課程改革的理念來統領。

sentences.english: And over the host of the tribe of the children of Issachar was Nethaneel the son of Zuar.
sentences.chinese: 統領以薩迦支派軍隊的是蘇押的兒子拿坦業。

sentences.english: Reason, your viceroy in me, me should defend.
sentences.chinese: 統領我的理智，本當將我衛護。

sentences.english: Also, in the Mayan tradition the number Nine plays a predominating role.
sentences.chinese: 此外，在傳統的瑪雅數字九統領作用的發揮。

sentences.english: Arkath gathers the Dwarves, grim masters of forge and fire.
sentences.chinese: 阿爾卡斯統領着矮人，是火焰與鑄造的大師。

sentences.english: But few think the 46-year-old lawmaker is running the show.
sentences.chinese: 但很少有人認爲，這名46歲的議員正在統領全局。

sentences.english: His boots and purple beret identify him as commanding the Scottish Paratroops.
sentences.chinese: 他的長靴和紫色貝雷帽表明他統領着蘇格蘭傘兵部隊。

sentences.english: And over the host of the tribe of the children of Gad was Eliasaph the son of Deuel.
sentences.chinese: 統領迦得支派軍隊的是丟珥的兒子以利雅薩。

sentences.english: And over the host of the tribe of the children of Manasseh was Gamaliel the son of Pedahzur.
sentences.chinese: 統領瑪拿西支派軍隊的是比大蓿的兒子迦瑪列。

sentences.english: And over the host of the tribe of the children of Simeon was Shelumiel the son of Zurishaddai.
sentences.chinese: 統領西緬支派軍隊的是蘇利沙代的兒子示路蔑。

sentences.english: Together the Cossack Hetmanate and Tsardom of Moscow march on the Polish Republic.
sentences.chinese: 如今，哥薩克統領與沙皇一起向波蘭共和國進軍。

sentences.english: Other laws, black on white, obtain.
sentences.chinese: 另有法令，白紙黑字，統領此地。

sentences.english: and Eliab son of Helon was over the division of the tribe of Zebulun.
sentences.chinese: 統領瑪拿西支派軍隊的是比大蓿的兒子迦瑪列。

sentences.english: The Phenomenology is attached to this system and ordered under it.
sentences.chinese: 現象學附屬於這個體系並且在其統領之下。

sentences.english: Shanghai is well-positioned to dominate globally as an innovation and knowledge economy, Schleicher told me.
sentences.chinese: 上海的創新和知識經濟，正摩厲以須，統領全球。

sentences.english: and Ahira son of Enan was over the division of the tribe of Naphtali.
sentences.chinese: 統領西緬支派軍隊的是蘇利沙代的兒子示路蔑。
